has the resources it needs-

00:07:54.870 --> 00:07:56.630
[Applause] All right, there we go.

00:07:56.630 --> 00:07:59.610 position:56%
I'm working to make sure that
Gallaudet has the resources it needs

00:07:59.610 --> 00:08:05.490 position:56%
