the one where we live.

00:34:27.790 --> 00:34:32.330 position:56%
We seek to how we can have that same
feeling of having full engagement

00:34:32.330 --> 00:34:34.630
in the broader world
around us and not just

00:34:34.630 --> 00:34:36.780
