00:34:55.140 --> 00:35:00.170
the Arabic speaking families,
the German speaking families,

00:35:00.170 --> 00:35:03.840
the French speaking families, all
of them coming together with us,

00:35:03.840 --> 00:35:07.760
thriving together in a
multi-lingual community.

00:35:07.760 --> 00:35:10.390
How can we make that happen?

00:35:10.390 --> 00:35:14.350 position:56%
These are the questions that we have
